<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-GB">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Consumer Duty Outcome Testing Report: {{ model_card.model_name }}</title>
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        @media print {
            body { background: #fff; font-size: 11px; }
            .no-print { display: none; }
            .section { break-inside: avoid; }
            .report-header { border-radius: 0; }
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
        .report-header {
            background: #1a1a2e;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .report-header h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
        .report-header .subtitle { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .header-meta {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
        }
        .header-meta-item { color: #94a3b8; }
        .header-meta-item strong { color: #e2e8f0; }
        .rag-banner {
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
        }
        .rag-green { background: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; }
        .rag-amber { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
        .rag-red   { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }
        .rag-dot { width: 14px; height: 14px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .dot-green { background: #059669; }
        .dot-amber { background: #d97706; }
        .dot-red   { background: #dc2626; }
        .section {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .section-header {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }
        .section-header h2 { font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; color: #1e293b; }
        .section-number {
            width: 24px; height: 24px;
            background: #1a1a2e; color: #fff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .section-body { padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; }
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.8125rem; }
        th {
            background: #f8fafc;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #475569;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        td { padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; vertical-align: top; }
        tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
        tr:hover td { background: #f8fafc; }
        tr.row-fail td { background: #fff5f5; }
        tr.row-fail:hover td { background: #fee2e2; }
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.125rem 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.025em;
        }
        .badge-pass     { background: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; }
        .badge-fail     { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }
        .badge-info     { background: #dbeafe; color: #1e40af; }
        .badge-warning  { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
        .badge-critical { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }
        .badge-price-value { background: #ede9fe; color: #5b21b6; }
        .badge-claims   { background: #dbeafe; color: #1e40af; }
        .badge-support  { background: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; }
        .badge-vuln     { background: #fce7f3; color: #9d174d; }
        .card-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        .card-label { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
        .card-value { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #1e293b; }
        .metric-value { font-family: 'Consolas', 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.8125rem; }
        .summary-stats { display: flex; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .stat-block { text-align: center; }
        .stat-number { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; }
        .stat-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #64748b; margin-top: 0.25rem; }
        .stat-pass { color: #059669; }
        .stat-fail { color: #dc2626; }
        .stat-warn { color: #d97706; }
        .corrective-actions { margin-top: 0.5rem; padding-left: 1.25rem; }
        .corrective-actions li { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: #991b1b; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
        .details-text { color: #475569; font-size: 0.8125rem; max-width: 600px; }
        .vuln-box {
            background: #fdf2f8;
            border: 1px solid #f9a8d4;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .vuln-box strong { color: #9d174d; }
        .run-id { font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #94a3b8; }
        .report-footer {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .report-header { padding: 1.25rem; }
            .section-body { padding: 1rem; }
            .card-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

    <!-- Report header -->
    <div class="report-header">
        <h1>Consumer Duty Outcome Testing Report</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">{{ model_card.model_name }} v{{ model_card.version }} &mdash; FCA PRIN 2A outcome monitoring</div>
        <div class="header-meta">
            <div class="header-meta-item"><strong>Period:</strong> {{ period }}</div>
            <div class="header-meta-item"><strong>Generated:</strong> {{ generated_date }}</div>
            <div class="header-meta-item"><strong>Model ID:</strong> {{ model_card.model_id }}</div>
            <div class="header-meta-item"><strong>Portfolio:</strong> {{ model_card.portfolio_scope or 'Not specified' }}</div>
            {% if model_card.monitoring_owner %}<div class="header-meta-item"><strong>Owner:</strong> {{ model_card.monitoring_owner }}</div>{% endif %}
            <div class="header-meta-item"><strong>Run ID:</strong> <span class="run-id">{{ run_id }}</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RAG status banner -->
    {% if rag_status == 'red' %}
    <div class="rag-banner rag-red">
        <span class="rag-dot dot-red"></span>
        OUTCOME STATUS: RED &mdash; Critical findings require immediate action and board escalation.
    </div>
    {% elif rag_status == 'amber' %}
    <div class="rag-banner rag-amber">
        <span class="rag-dot dot-amber"></span>
        OUTCOME STATUS: AMBER &mdash; Warning findings require documented remediation plan.
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <div class="rag-banner rag-green">
        <span class="rag-dot dot-green"></span>
        OUTCOME STATUS: GREEN &mdash; All outcome tests passed within thresholds.
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- SECTION 1: Executive Summary -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-number">1</div>
            <h2>Executive Summary</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="section-body">
            {% set n_pass = results | selectattr('passed', 'equalto', true) | list | length %}
            {% set n_fail = results | selectattr('passed', 'equalto', false) | list | length %}
            {% set n_critical = results | selectattr('severity', 'equalto', 'critical') | selectattr('passed', 'equalto', false) | list | length %}
            {% set n_warning = results | selectattr('severity', 'equalto', 'warning') | selectattr('passed', 'equalto', false) | list | length %}

            <div class="summary-stats">
                <div class="stat-block">
                    <div class="stat-number">{{ results | length }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Total Tests</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-block">
                    <div class="stat-number stat-pass">{{ n_pass }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Passed</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-block">
                    <div class="stat-number stat-fail">{{ n_fail }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Failed</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-block">
                    <div class="stat-number stat-fail">{{ n_critical }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Critical</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-block">
                    <div class="stat-number stat-warn">{{ n_warning }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Warnings</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-grid">
                <div>
                    <div class="card-label">Reporting Period</div>
                    <div class="card-value">{{ period }}</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="card-label">Model</div>
                    <div class="card-value">{{ model_card.model_name }} v{{ model_card.version }}</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="card-label">Model Class</div>
                    <div class="card-value">{{ model_card.model_class | title }}</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="card-label">Overall RAG</div>
                    <div class="card-value"><span class="badge badge-{{ rag_status }}">{{ rag_status | upper }}</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- SECTION 2: All Outcome Test Results -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-number">2</div>
            <h2>Outcome Test Results</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="section-body">
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Outcome Area</th>
                        <th>Test Name</th>
                        <th>Segment</th>
                        <th>Status</th>
                        <th>Metric</th>
                        <th>Threshold</th>
                        <th>Severity</th>
                        <th>Details</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                {% for r in results %}
                <tr class="{{ 'row-fail' if not r.passed else '' }}">
                    <td><span class="badge badge-{{ r.outcome | replace('_', '-') }}">{{ r.outcome | replace('_', ' ') | title }}</span></td>
                    <td><span class="metric-value">{{ r.test_name }}</span></td>
                    <td>{{ r.segment or '&mdash;' }}</td>
                    <td><span class="badge {{ 'badge-pass' if r.passed else 'badge-fail' }}">{{ 'PASS' if r.passed else 'FAIL' }}</span></td>
                    <td><span class="metric-value">{{ '%.4f' | format(r.metric_value) if r.metric_value is not none else '&mdash;' }}</span></td>
                    <td><span class="metric-value">{{ '%.4f' | format(r.threshold) if r.threshold is not none else '&mdash;' }}</span></td>
                    <td><span class="badge badge-{{ r.severity }}">{{ r.severity | upper }}</span></td>
                    <td class="details-text">{{ r.details }}</td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- SECTION 3: Failed Tests and Corrective Actions -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    {% set failed_results = results | selectattr('passed', 'equalto', false) | list %}
    {% if failed_results %}
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-number">3</div>
            <h2>Failed Tests and Corrective Actions</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="section-body">
            {% for r in failed_results %}
            <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
                    <span class="badge badge-{{ r.outcome | replace('_', '-') }}">{{ r.outcome | replace('_', ' ') | title }}</span>
                    <strong style="font-size: 0.875rem;">{{ r.test_name }}</strong>
                    {% if r.segment %}<span class="badge badge-info">{{ r.segment }}</span>{% endif %}
                    <span class="badge badge-{{ r.severity }}">{{ r.severity | upper }}</span>
                </div>
                <p class="details-text" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">{{ r.details }}</p>
                {% if r.corrective_actions %}
                <div style="font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #991b1b; margin-top: 0.5rem;">Required Actions:</div>
                <ul class="corrective-actions">
                    {% for action in r.corrective_actions %}
                    <li>{{ action }}</li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ul>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- SECTION 4: Vulnerable Customer Results -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    {% set vuln_results = results | selectattr('segment', 'defined') | selectattr('segment', 'ne', none) | list %}
    {% if vuln_results %}
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-number">4</div>
            <h2>Segmented Results</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="section-body">
            <div class="vuln-box">
                <strong>Note:</strong> Results below are segment-specific. Vulnerable customer segments
                require enhanced scrutiny under FCA Consumer Duty (PRIN 2A.2.3G) — firms must consider
                the particular needs of customers who may be in vulnerable circumstances.
            </div>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Segment</th>
                        <th>Outcome Area</th>
                        <th>Test Name</th>
                        <th>Status</th>
                        <th>Metric</th>
                        <th>Threshold</th>
                        <th>Details</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                {% for r in vuln_results %}
                <tr class="{{ 'row-fail' if not r.passed else '' }}">
                    <td><span class="badge badge-vuln">{{ r.segment }}</span></td>
                    <td><span class="badge badge-{{ r.outcome | replace('_', '-') }}">{{ r.outcome | replace('_', ' ') | title }}</span></td>
                    <td><span class="metric-value">{{ r.test_name }}</span></td>
                    <td><span class="badge {{ 'badge-pass' if r.passed else 'badge-fail' }}">{{ 'PASS' if r.passed else 'FAIL' }}</span></td>
                    <td><span class="metric-value">{{ '%.4f' | format(r.metric_value) if r.metric_value is not none else '&mdash;' }}</span></td>
                    <td><span class="metric_value">{{ '%.4f' | format(r.threshold) if r.threshold is not none else '&mdash;' }}</span></td>
                    <td class="details-text">{{ r.details }}</td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="report-footer">
        <span>Consumer Duty Outcome Testing Report &mdash; {{ model_card.model_name }} &mdash; Period: {{ period }}</span>
        <span>Run ID: <span class="run-id">{{ run_id }}</span></span>
        <span>Generated: {{ generated_date }}</span>
    </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
